** Project Description
LINE Pay for FluentCart is a payment gateway for FluentCart that integrate LINE Pay payment with FluentCart.


** Features
 - one time payment
 - admin setting
 - sandbox mode
 - Support Taiwan only
 - refund (including partial refund)
 - transaction logging


** Coding convension
 - using composer to load class

** folder structure
 - wpbr-fluentcart-linepay
   - src
     - Settings
     - Gateways
   - assets
     - js
     - css

